### ========================================
### [STEP 1] 이메일 인증 발송 (인증번호 요청)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "moonjg0305@yu.ac.kr"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 2] 인증번호 검증 (메일로 받은 6자리 입력)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "moonjg0305@yu.ac.kr",
  "code": "736107"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 3] 회원가입 (인증 완료 후 즉시 가입)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "22112052",
  "name": "문진곤",
  "email": "moonjg0305@yu.ac.kr",
  "password": "mypassword123"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 4] 로그인 → JWT 토큰 발급
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "moonjg0305@yu.ac.kr",
  "password": "mypassword123"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 5] 내 프로필 조회 (JWT 토큰 필요)
### ========================================
# 💡 로그인 응답에서 받은 token 값을 아래 Bearer 뒤에 붙여넣으세요
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

### ========================================
### [STEP 6] 매너 온도 갱신 (JWT 토큰 필요)
### ========================================
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/manner
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

{
  "score": 0.5
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 7] 동승 방 개설 (JWT 토큰 필요)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

{
  "title": "영대 정문에서 대구은행역 가실 분",
  "departure": "영남대 정문",
  "destination": "대구은행역",
  "departureTime": "21:30",
  "maxParticipants": 4,
  "userId": "22112052"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 8] 자동 매칭 테스트 (매칭 성공 시나리오)
### ========================================
# 먼저 STEP 7 방 개설이 살아있는 상태에서 실행해야 합니다.
# 목적지를 "반월당역"으로 다르게 보냈지만, 대구은행역과 직선거리가 약 1.4km라
# 유사도가 약 81%로 계산되어 기존 방에 자동으로 합류(MATCHED)되어야 합니다.
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/rooms/match
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

{
  "userId": "22119999",
  "title": "시내 방향 가실 분 구함",
  "departure": "영남대 정문",
  "destination": "반월당역",
  "departureTime": "21:30"
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 9] 탑승 완료 처리 (WAITING/FULL → COMPLETED)
### ========================================
# roomId는 STEP 7 응답에서 받은 값으로 교체하세요
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/rooms/77f28106/complete
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

### ========================================
### [STEP 10] 방 취소 (방장만 가능, WAITING/FULL → CANCELLED)
### ========================================
# roomId는 새로 개설한 방의 값으로 교체하세요
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/rooms/77f28106/cancel
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

### ========================================
### [STEP 11] 정산 시작 (COMPLETED 상태 방에서만 가능)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/payments/77f28106
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

{
  "totalFare": 12000
}

### ========================================
### [STEP 12] 내 납부 처리 (JWT 토큰 필요)
### ========================================
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/payments/77f28106/pay
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE

### ========================================
### [STEP 13] 정산 현황 조회
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/payments/77f28106
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyMjExMjA1MiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTEwNzE3MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMTkzNTcyfQ.QKn9FfMvGcrJ7P9CzJSQ7uTwDRKFqIczCZl_e0m0xEE